widgets_values:
This workflow helps you compare up to six SDXL fine tunes focused on photorealism.

Differently from a standard XY Plot, this workflow compares:

- each SDXL fine-tune configured according to the model's author recommendations (not an apple-to-apple comparison)

- each SDXL fine-tune configured according to Alessandro's recommendation (a non-optimized apple-to-apple comparison)

- each SDXL fine-tune configured according to your preferred settings.


If you need to perform more sophisticated experiments, I recommend using my AP Workflow 10 and its XYZ Plot function:
https://perilli.com/ai/comfyui/

widgets_values: Cinematic film still of a brave firefighter, muscular and determined, early 30s, Caucasian, short brown hair, his face smeared with soot, sweat glistening in the low-key lighting, framed by towering flames and thick smoke. The shot captures a mid-action scene in an urban setting, with a handheld camera capturing the intensity and chaos. The firefighter is in full gear, his eyes focused and unwavering, holding a heavy hose aimed at the roaring fire. The background shows burning debris and collapsing structures, with a dynamic play of shadows and light, emphasizing the urgency and danger of the scene, shot with a Canon EOS C300 Mark III, 4k resolution, dramatic and immersive.
